The '''Circle''' was the center of [[Tahv]], the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kesh/Legends|Kesh]]. Inside the Circle lay the [[Kesh capitol building|capitol building]] and the [[Circle Chambers]], where the [[Lost Tribe of Sith]]'s ruling council, the [[Circle of Lords]], convened.

